  [  0] pusharglist 0 ........................... <>
  [  2] localcall 2 ............................. <getVariableManager()>
  [  4] getparam 0 .............................. <tID>
  [  6] getparam 1 .............................. <tValue>
  [  8] pusharglist 3 ........................... <getVariableManager(), tID, tValue>
  [ 10] objcall 164 ............................. <getVariableManager().create(tID, tValue)>
  [ 12] pusharglistnoret 1 ...................... <getVariableManager().create(tID, tValue)>
  [ 14] extcall 11 .............................. return getVariableManager().create(tID, tValue)
  [ 16] ret
end

